{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"title":"targetCoordinate","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value other than "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserTrackingMode/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse":{"title":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnusertrackingmode\/mlnusertrackingmodefollowwithcourse","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The map follows the user location and rotates when the course changes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Course represents the direction in which the device is traveling."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default user location annotation shows a puck-shaped indicator"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that rotates as the course changes."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":{"fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"targetCoordinate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"location is being tracked.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"}}}